 99^99) ≡ 8 (mod 10).\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"By steps 3 and 4, the sum is congruent to 9 + 9 = 18, and 18 ≡ 8 modulo 10.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"step 3\",\n        \"step 4\",\n        \"modular arithmetic\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"final_answer\": \"8\"\n}\n\nProduce the JSON formalization."
