laim\": \"(2005^2 + 2005^0 + 2005^0 + 2005^5) % 100 = 52.\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"The modulo 100 remainder of the expression is the unique integer between 0 and 99 congruent to it modulo 100, and step 5 shows that residue is 52.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"step 5\",\n        \"definition of remainder modulo 100\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"final_answer\": \"52\"\n}\n\nProduce the JSON formalization."
