maining possibility is b - 4 = 0.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"step 3\",\n        \"step 4\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"claim\": \"b = 4.\",\n      \"reasoning\": \"Adding 4 to both sides of b - 4 = 0 yields b = 4.\",\n      \"facts_used\": [\n        \"step 5\",\n        \"addition property of equality\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"final_answer\": \"4\"\n}\n\nProduce the JSON formalization."
